  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->

  <section class="section hiw-section" id="how-it-works">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-eyebrow reveal">
        <div class="section-eyebrow-line"></div>
        <span>The Process</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Three steps.<br>Done forever.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub reveal">If you've sold on Facebook Marketplace and hated every second of it — this is the antidote.</p>

```
  <div class="hiw-grid">
    <div class="hiw-step reveal">
      <div class="hiw-num">01</div>
      <div class="hiw-icon">📸</div>
      <div class="hiw-title">Upload & Quote</div>
      <p class="hiw-desc">Take a few photos on your phone. Tell us the brand, condition, and category. We'll send you a fair quote — fast. No negotiation, no drama.</p>
      <div class="hiw-time">⏱ Under 5 minutes</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hiw-step reveal reveal-d1">
      <div class="hiw-num">02</div>
      <div class="hiw-icon">📦</div>
      <div class="hiw-title">Ship It Free</div>
      <p class="hiw-desc">Accept the quote and we'll email you a prepaid shipping label. Box it up and drop it off. Or order our Stuff-Simplify Kit™ for even easier packing.</p>
      <div class="hiw-time">⏱ Drop off in minutes</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hiw-step reveal reveal-d2">
      <div class="hiw-num">03</div>
      <div class="hiw-icon">💸</div>
      <div class="hiw-title">Get Paid</div>
      <p class="hiw-desc">We verify your item and send payment within 48 hours of receipt — via Venmo, PayPal, or direct deposit. We handle listing, selling, and shipping from there.</p>
      <div class="hiw-time">⏱ Paid in 48 hours</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
